text: Jugaadi Dot Com (2015) is a Punjabi romantic comedy film directed by Anil Vij, starring Nachhatar Gill, Feroz Khan, Sarb Chawla, Rana Ranbir, Mansi Sharma, Komya Virk, Megha Sharma, Ghulle Shah, Bhotu Shah, Parkash Gaadu, Dr.Ranjit Riyaz, Cheeku, Babbu Gill, Honey Shergill, Vishv Dipak Trikha and Gajendra Phogat. ==Cast== * Ehtisham Ahmed * Nachhatar Gill * Feroz Khan * Sarb Chawla * Rana Ranbir * Mansi Sharma * Komya Virk * Megha Sharma *Ghulle Shah *Bhotu Shah *Parkash Gaadu *Dr.Ranjit Riyaz *Cheeku *Babbu Gill *Honey Shergill *Vishv Dipak Trikha Gajendra Phogat *Ashish Rana ==Reception== ==References== ==External links== * Facebook page Category:2015 films Category:Indian films Category:2010s Punjabi-language films
